metadata.name: Start to body symbology
metadata.description:
In words of Parecelsus: ..." There is a star in the man for every star in the sky" and because there is a star inside him ,man can find his counterpart in the universe; and because he has this star in his own soul, man can understand and fuse his RATIONAL and EMOTIONAL energies with those more distant in the universe".

Acrylic on canvas  
2022
